Weapon infobox, implemented in [[Module:Infobox]] and stored in the Cargo table <code>weapons</code>.

See [[Template:WeaponInfobox/Skills|/Skills]] for the automatic Skill linking part of the template.<br>
See [[Template:WeaponInfobox/Resource|/Resource]] for the automatic resource node linking part of the template.

Example usage:
<pre>
{{WeaponInfobox
| title = Copper Sword
| image =
| description = An all-round weapon that deals slash damage and has a greater effect on vegetation and thickets.
| structure = Crafting
| weapon_type = Sword
| gear_level = 9
| physical_power = 8.5
| stats = +25% Physical Damage to Vegetation
| durability = 1085
| salvageable = 12 [[Copper Ingot]]<br/>9 [[Plank]]
}}
</pre>
